caption.p: Effects of the wampee extracts on total glutathione. Cells were treated with the different wampee extracts (1000 μg/ml) in combination with H 2O 2 (1 mM) for 3 h Total glutathione was measured. Values and error bars indicate the mean glutathione level and standard deviations, respectively. Data were expressed as the means ± SD of three independent experiments. The values were grouped alphabetically by one-way ANOVA analysis ( p < 0.05).
